channel.title: [317] Allstar Based Source [317]
channel.description:
Hey, I am the owner of str pker scape, allstar based source, and what you guys know. oh allstar sucks. honestly guys its our opinion and plus allstars can go far if you make them stable like some of them, what i am doing now is a new project based off of my old source, what i am planing to do is make some updates with the server and everything, look below.
~Bash mini game( drops all the rares in the server ) ~ Gwd ( i want this to drop all the bandos pieces, i want it to drop bgs and armadyl) ~A full 100% anti nuller and anti. ( all i have is really a 75% anti nuller and a 0% anti dupe) ~i want to make slayer so you have to kill the monsters for exp. ~i also want a dark bow mini ~Cwars( i have c wars, but i want waiting rooms, and the flags taken 100%) ~Items that change you into npcs (sythe, monkey gree gree, tiara to change you into a "thing") <-- this isnt my idea a saw it off a server
These are some of the things i personaly want, you guys can add comments below, but i also need some of your guy's help, I need a highly experienced coder for allstar, like as good as mabey rage, or paradox, or Iceman who can be next to me to code, or just to code some cool things in skills, and stuff like that. So i was wondering if you guys can help me code an amazing server and help me reach that goal of that amazing allstar server that always has 20 players on like futurescape.so i am just begging one of you people out there can help me do this and make 1 of my dreams become a reality, btw that dosnt mean i have no life, i do. ~Thanks for Reading. ~Str Pker
